msgid ""
"If the contents aren't suitable for a ``note::``, you can also use ``tabs::"
"``. We are using `sphinx-tabs`_, however since `sphinx-design`_ also "
"provides tabs, it should be noted that we don't use that feature of sphinx-"
"design."
